---
By: Tripura Rahasya
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 68
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Consciousness
---
There can be nothing but consciousness. Tell me any place where there is no
consciousness; there is no place beyond consciousness. Or can anyone prove
in any manner anything outside consciousness? Consciousness is inescapable.
